[package]
name = "nod"
version = "2.0.0-alpha.4"
edition = "2024"
rust-version = "1.85"
authors = [ "Luke Street <luke@street.dev>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/encounter/nod"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/nod"
readme = "../README.md"
description = "Library for reading and writing GameCube and Wii disc images.\n"
keywords = [ "gamecube", "wii", "iso", "wbfs", "rvz",]
categories = [ "command-line-utilities", "parser-implementations",]

[features]
default = [ "compress-bzip2", "compress-lzma", "compress-zlib", "compress-zstd", "threading",]
compress-bzip2 = [ "bzip2",]
compress-lzma = [ "liblzma", "liblzma-sys",]
compress-zlib = [ "adler2", "miniz_oxide",]
compress-zstd = [ "zstd", "zstd-safe",]
openssl = [ "dep:openssl",]
openssl-vendored = [ "openssl", "openssl/vendored",]
threading = [ "dep:crossbeam-channel", "dep:crossbeam-utils",]

[dependencies]
aes = "0.9.0-rc.1"
crypto-common = "=0.2.0-rc.13"
base16ct = "0.3"
block-padding = "=0.4.0-rc.4"
bytes = "1.10"
cbc = "0.2.0-rc.1"
crc32fast = "1.5"
dyn-clone = "1.0"
encoding_rs = "0.8"
itertools = "0.14"
lru = "0.16"
polonius-the-crab = "0.4"
simple_moving_average = "1.0"
thiserror = "2.0"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.adler2]
version = "2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.bzip2]
version = "0.6"
features = [ "static",]
optional = true

[dependencies.crossbeam-channel]
version = "0.5"
optional = true

[dependencies.crossbeam-utils]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.digest]
version = "0.11.0-rc.3"
default-features = false

[dependencies.liblzma]
version = "0.4"
features = [ "static",]
optional = true

[dependencies.liblzma-sys]
version = "0.4"
features = [ "static",]
optional = true

[dependencies.md-5]
version = "0.11.0-rc.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.miniz_oxide]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.openssl]
version = "0.10"
optional = true

[dependencies.sha1]
version = "0.11.0-rc.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh64",]

[dependencies.zerocopy]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "alloc", "derive",]

[dependencies.zstd]
version = "0.13"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.zstd-safe]
version = "7.2"
optional = true
default-features = false
